item.title: 【SD Live Performances】Kylie Minogue - Sydney Entertainment Centre, Sydney, Australia, 11-05-2001-caladan [568p]
item.description:
I processed the main concert of the Live in Sydney DVD: deinterlaced with QTGMC, deblocked, slightly denoised, resized (correct aspect ratio), cropped the black bars. I converted the video to MP4 AVC - CRF18 and the audio to AAC 224kbps. I added song titles to each chapter too.
